data.description: The home is nestled in the middle of a private  cedar forest located within a short walk to Killebrew Lake/trails. The land is improved wIth open spaces for blue sky gazing and fenced garden area. The home has been updated throughout:flooring, interior/exterior paint, induction oven, decking. Large main ensuite w/added room for office/exercise and walk-in closet. Two guest bedrooms and full guest bath located at the opposite end of the home ensures privacy for all. Open floor plan and large picture windows gives space an open, airy feeling filled with natural light. The kitchen has a breakfast counter and cozy nook area for tea time and planning. Large garage/shop with bonus storage area above. This is a must see to appreciate property.
